This is not remotely intended to be nasty, so I apologize in advance if it comes across that way to you: the people (like me) who wuld be interested in this do not require other information- we are interested in scientific phenomena and their measurements AND we know who Grace is (was) so all necessary to let us know to go was there. It is highly unlikely someone not in one or both of those categories would be interested, though not impossible. <img src="http://forums.randi.org/images/smilies/smile.gif"/>
